original_title: Travis Decker search: New evidence shows he is the only suspect in his daughters’ killings, sheriff’s office says | CNN
article_summary: "Washington man Travis Decker is the sole suspect in the deaths of his three daughters, aged 5 to 9, according to investigators. DNA evidence found at the crime scene matches Decker's profile, and no other DNA was discovered. The girls' bodies were found near a campsite in the Cascades in May, and Decker has been on the run since."</s>
